      "title": "Calculate the total mass",
      "content": "To find the mean mass, sum all the individual masses. Adding 4,010 + 4,010 + 3,030 + 4,050 + 3,050 step-by-step: <ul><li>4,010 + 4,010 = 8,020</li><li>8,020 + 3,030 = 11,050</li><li>11,050 + 4,050 = 15,100</li><li>15,100 + 3,050 = 18,150</li></ul> Total mass = 18,150 grams."
